  <h1>Hero Section</h1>
  <p class="lead">Hero patterns using layout-cover for vertical centering. Responsive without media queries.</p>

  <section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <p>Hero sections are prominent page areas that introduce content with a headline, supporting text, and call-to-action buttons. This snippet uses <code>&lt;layout-cover&gt;</code> for vertical centering, <code>&lt;layout-center&gt;</code> for horizontal alignment, and semantic <code>&lt;nav&gt;</code> with <code>&lt;ul&gt;</code> for CTA button groups.</p>
      <p><strong>Key features:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Vertical centering with <code>layout-cover</code></li>
        <li>Configurable minimum height</li>
        <li>Semantic <code>&lt;nav&gt;</code> for CTA links — <code>data-layout="cluster"</code> on the <code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></li>
        <li>Centered and split layout variants</li>
        <li>Optional background image support</li>
        <li>Responsive without media queries</li>
      </ul>
    </layout-text>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Basic Hero</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <p>A centered hero with headline, lead text, and action buttons.</p>
    </layout-text>

    <browser-window
      src="/docs/snippets/demos/hero-basic.html"
      url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/hero-basic"
      title="Basic Hero"
      shadow>
    </browser-window>

    <code-block language="html" label="Basic centered hero">&lt;section class="hero"&gt;
  &lt;layout-cover data-layout-min="60vh" data-layout-padding="xl"&gt;
    &lt;layout-center data-layout-max="normal"&gt;
      &lt;layout-stack data-layout-gap="l" class="hero-content"&gt;
        &lt;h1&gt;Build Beautiful Interfaces&lt;/h1&gt;
        &lt;p class="lead"&gt;
          A lightweight CSS framework built on modern standards.
          No JavaScript required for core functionality.
        &lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;nav&gt;
          &lt;ul data-layout="cluster" data-layout-justify="center" data-layout-gap="m"&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="/get-started/" class="button"&gt;Get Started&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="/docs/" class="button secondary"&gt;Documentation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
          &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/nav&gt;
      &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
    &lt;/layout-center&gt;
  &lt;/layout-cover&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;</code-block>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Split Layout Hero</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <p>A hero with text on one side and an image on the other, using <code>layout-sidebar</code>.</p>
    </layout-text>

    <browser-window
      src="/docs/snippets/demos/hero-split.html"
      url="https://vanilla-breeze.dev/hero-split"
      title="Split Hero"
      shadow>
    </browser-window>

    <code-block language="html" label="Split layout hero">&lt;section class="hero"&gt;
  &lt;layout-cover data-layout-min="50vh" data-layout-padding="xl"&gt;
    &lt;layout-sidebar data-layout-gap="2xl" data-layout-sidebar-width="wide" data-layout-content-min="50"&gt;
      &lt;layout-stack data-layout-gap="l"&gt;
        &lt;layout-badge data-variant="info"&gt;New Release&lt;/layout-badge&gt;
        &lt;h1&gt;Feature Announcement&lt;/h1&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;
          Detailed description of the feature or product.
          Highlight key benefits and unique selling points.
        &lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;nav&gt;
          &lt;ul data-layout="cluster" data-layout-gap="m"&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="/learn-more/" class="button"&gt;Learn More&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="/demo/" class="button ghost"&gt;Watch Demo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
          &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/nav&gt;
      &lt;/layout-stack&gt;
      &lt;img
        src="/images/feature.png"
        alt="Feature illustration"
        width="600"
        height="400"
        loading="eager"&gt;
    &lt;/layout-sidebar&gt;
  &lt;/layout-cover&gt;
&lt;/section&gt;</code-block>
  </section>

